Developer Terms of Use
des:
This study is aimed to test the effects of voice on user satisfaction with various types of system responses and the effect of voice on user perceptions of system personality.

This skill will be used to collect data for a research project conducted by the Pratt Institute team. The study aims to investigate user preferences for Alexa personality and is approved by IRB (#9142019-AD-IL). The skill is a supplement to an instruction form that is used by volunteer participants recruited from the Pratt Institute community.
